<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
<link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
<link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap-icons/1.10.5/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lato&family=Merriweather&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
    body {
        font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
        background-color: #ceedec;
    }

    h3, h6 {
        font-family: 'Merriweather', serif;
        color: #242f66;
    }

    .text-primary {
        color: #07a6a6 !important;
    }

    .faq-icon {
        color: #07a6a6;
    }

    .faq-card {
        background-color: white;
        border-radius: 10px;
        padding: 20px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: space-between;
        height: 100%;
    }
</style>

<!-- FAQ Section -->
@page "/faq"
<NavComponent></NavComponent>
<section class="py-5">
    <h3 class="text-center mb-4 pb-2 fw-bold">Frequently Asked Questions</h3>
    <p class="text-center mb-5">
        Have questions about our printing services? Find quick answers below.
    </p>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="row g-4">

            <!-- Each column is now a flex container to make all cards equal height -->
            <div class="col-md-4 d-flex">
                <div class="faq-card w-100">
                    <h6><i class="fas fa-print faq-icon pe-2"></i>What printing services do you offer?</h6>
                    <p>We offer business cards, flyers, brochures, banners, posters, booklets, and more—both digital and offset printing options available.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4 d-flex">
                <div class="faq-card w-100">
                    <h6><i class="fas fa-upload faq-icon pe-2"></i>How do I upload my design?</h6>
                    <p>You can upload your files directly on our website while placing your order. We support PDF, JPG, PNG, and AI formats.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4 d-flex">
                <div class="faq-card w-100">
                    <h6><i class="fas fa-sync-alt faq-icon pe-2"></i>Can I make changes after placing an order?</h6>
                    <p>If your order hasn't gone to print, you can still make edits. Contact our support team ASAP for adjustments.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4 d-flex">
                <div class="faq-card w-100">
                    <h6><i class="fas fa-clock faq-icon pe-2"></i>What is the turnaround time?</h6>
                    <p>Standard orders are completed within 3–5 business days. Express service is available for next-day delivery on select products.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4 d-flex">
                <div class="faq-card w-100">
                    <h6><i class="fas fa-truck faq-icon pe-2"></i>Do you offer delivery?</h6>
                    <p>Yes, we deliver across Pakistan. Delivery charges and time depend on your location and order size.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4 d-flex">
                <div class="faq-card w-100">
                    <h6><i class="fas fa-dollar-sign faq-icon pe-2"></i>What are your payment options?</h6>
                    <p>We accept payments via credit/debit cards, bank transfers, Easypaisa, and JazzCash.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4 d-flex">
                <div class="faq-card w-100">
                    <h6><i class="fas fa-search faq-icon pe-2"></i>Do you offer design templates?</h6>
                    <p>Yes! We provide free customizable templates for business cards, flyers, and brochures on our website.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4 d-flex">
                <div class="faq-card w-100">
                    <h6><i class="fas fa-question-circle faq-icon pe-2"></i>What if I'm not satisfied with the print quality?</h6>
                    <p>If you're unhappy with your order, we offer reprints or refunds depending on the issue. Your satisfaction is guaranteed.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4 d-flex">
                <div class="faq-card w-100">
                    <h6><i class="fas fa-phone faq-icon pe-2"></i>How can I contact customer support?</h6>
                    <p>You can reach us via live chat, email, or our customer service number from 9 AM to 9 PM, Monday to Saturday.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>
